<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Questions</div>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What's the dress code?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">Dress to impress for the nightclub. No flip-flops, sports jerseys, workout clothes, baseball caps, or offensive imagery. Smart casual or club attire works perfectly. No dress code is required to board the party bus.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is our group kept private the entire time?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">Absolutely. Your group is never paired with strangers. You get a private party bus, private time at the lounge, and your own nightclub entry — the entire experience is exclusively yours from start to finish.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can we bring our own drinks (BYOB)?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">Yes — the party bus is BYOB-friendly. We also provide complimentary champagne, mixers, cups, straws, napkins, and fresh ice. Responsible drinking is expected throughout the experience.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What if someone in our group is under 21?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">All participants must be 21+ with a valid ID. IDs are checked at three separate points during the experience. Exception: 21st birthday participants are welcome if the reservation is booked for midnight or later.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How far in advance should we book?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">At least 1–2 weeks for a regular weekend. For major events (EDC, Memorial Day, 4th of July, NYE, large conferences) book 4–6 weeks ahead — those dates sell out fast and we can't guarantee availability last-minute.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can we choose which nightclub we go to?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">You can express a preference and we'll do our best to accommodate it. Available clubs rotate by day based on schedules and special events. Our team always selects the best available option for your date. Use the club finder above to see what's typically open.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Where do you pick us up?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">We pick up at hotels, lounges, or event locations across Las Vegas, Henderson, Summerlin, Southwest Las Vegas, and North Las Vegas. Off-Strip and Airbnb pickups are accommodated (may slightly affect the itinerary timing).</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can we split the payment?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">Yes — payment can be split up to 3 ways. For larger groups, we can also accommodate individual payments. Contact us to arrange the best payment setup for your group.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

